### NduthiRide — Users endpoints
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@accessToken = <paste_access_token_here>

### ─── Get my profile ─────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ─── Update my profile ──────────────────────────────────────
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Jane Wanjiku Mwangi",
  "email": "jane@example.com"
}

### ─── Change password ────────────────────────────────────────
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/me/password
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "SecurePass123!",
  "newPassword": "NewSecurePass456!"
}

### ─── Upload avatar (multipart) ─────────────────────────────
### Use the REST Client File Upload feature or Swagger UI for this
### POST {{baseUrl}}/users/me/avatar
### Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
### Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary
